name: HALCYON EGG
description:
Art and Sound by Mike Neff. 8.8.2021

The Halcyon egg lives in memory between history and legend. Massive in size, this seminal piece of antiquity is said to have given birth to entire worlds. There are also those who believe that the Halcyon egg was the paragon of the hubris that caused The Fall, having given form to forces beyond anyone's control.

If this relic ever truly existed, it would now be somewhere in the liminal space with the rest of the great power that fell into the Void, and only those that dwell there can know. . . .
